rem Outside Cafe
rem 8/18/2017

do Examine Mei Ho Cafe
 [
  print Sitting outside under an awning, your contact from the Black Net reads 
  print a data stream off his phone. This is the building he told you to meet at 
  print after you found the sim chip. He doesn't seem to see you, but you can feel 
  print him watching.
 ]

do Enter Mei Ho Cafe
 [
  ifflag hosaka alarm
   [
    print Your contact looks up at you.
    print
    print "Looks like you pulled it off. I'm monitoring a local security channel, and
    print Hosaka is having a bit of an incident. I assume that was you. Good job, now
    print hand over the ram."
    go Mei Ho Cafe
   | 
    print Not without the ram, it would be unprofessional.
   ]
 ]

do Walk North
 [
  print You walk north to Hakaru Station.
  go Hakaru Station
 ]

do Walk South
 [
  print You walk south into a shaddier part of town, finding the only hotel in Ninsei.
  go Outside Hotel
 ]